Package ca.uwo.csteam14

Class Main

java.lang.Object
ca.uwo.csteam14.Main
public class Main extends Object
The Main class is the entry point of BuildingBuddy. Contains methods for getting optimum points, full names of floors and buildings, updating current POI, and changing security keys. Also has a method to restart the application.
Since:
2023-03-07
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jason B. Shew, Daniel Gomes, Robert Beemer, Arjuna Kadirgamar, Joshua Cini
